#. Tag: cmdsynopsis
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:26
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kalzium</command> <group><option>Options</option></group> <group "
"choice=\"opt\"><option>--molecule <replaceable>filename</replaceable></"
"option></group>"
msgstr ""
"<command>kalzium</command> <group><option>Opciones</option></group> <group "
"choice=\"opt\"><option>--molecule <replaceable>archivo</replaceable></"
"option></group>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descripción"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; is a program which shows you the Periodic System of the Elements "
"(PSE). You can use &kalzium; to search for information about the elements or "
"to learn facts about the PSE."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; es un programa que le muestra la tabla periódica de los elementos "
"(TPE). Puede usar &kalzium; para buscar información sobre los elementos o "
"para aprender cosas sobre la TPE."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kalzium; provides you with all kinds of information about the PSE. You can "
"look up lots of information about the elements and also use visualisations "
"to show them."
msgstr ""
"&kalzium; le proporciona todo tipo de información sobre la TPE. Puede "
"encontrar abundante información sobre los elementos y usar distintos tipos "
"de visualizaciones para mostrarla."

#. Tag: para
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "This package is part of the official KDE edutainment module."
msgstr "Este paquete es parte del módulo oficial educativo de KDE."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opciones"

#. Tag: option
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "--molecule <replaceable>filename</replaceable>"
msgstr "--molecule <replaceable>archivo</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kalzium.1.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the given molecule file in cml, xyz, ent, pdb, alc, chm, cdx, cdxml, "
"c3d1, c3d2, gpr, mdl, mol, sdf, sd, crk3d, cht, dmol, bgf, gam, inp, gamin, "
"gamout, tmol, fract, mpd, or mol2 format."
msgstr ""
"Abrir la molécula indicada en formato cml, xyz, ent, pdb, alc, chm, cdx, "
"cdxml, c3d1, c3d2, gpr, mdl, mol, sdf, sd, crk3d, cht, dmol, bgf, gam, inp, "
"gamin, gamout, tmol, fract, mpd o mol2."

